  = "Editing analysis of <br />%s - <em>%s</em>" % [@problem.code, @problem.name]

You can use a markup. Read about in 
%a{:href => "http://txt2tags.sourceforge.net/markup.html"} http://txt2tags.sourceforge.net/markup.html.
